{"tid":2028271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［頂置］有危便有機 文革批鬥係藍屍廢老最驚","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T19:12:58.000Z","uid":27203,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eab93c53dffd73de53b4bb9216edc19058dbbba8","tid":2028271,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"上年建制全力推送中條例 再加幾個月既浪潮<br />\n基本上民意基本盤變化唔會大得去邊<br />\n<br />\n今年到國安法 佢地一定盡力護航<br />\n而佢淨番既支持者一定係藍絲廢老 幾十年前比人批鬥落黎<br />\n<br />\n今次我地要做既就係將國安法包裝成文革2.0 <br />\n順便用呢一次瓦解成個少數派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之一提國安法就話民革重臨就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極端化係政治上拉攏支持者既重要手段 正如林奠將示威變恐怖主義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位連衛兵 文宣組 而家要做既一定係出大量文宣<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣揚文革2.0</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得周街文宣 瘋狂air drop同 洗Twitter ! 要做足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"5ae531d777894a7e617e1d2deb1b7938fc962070","tid":2028271,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"195e3ca3c0a13d583a63b9d69e7e47770d572426","tid":2028271,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6408b66fb1f11d676fe5853d246f85889d8bbcf","tid":2028271,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda129d997f29f9bfcde5a2ac6b941168c8f06c1","tid":2028271,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔好驚 要借力打力"},{"pid":"7be88cb